{"tid":2246690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人迫我去做狗","createTime":"2020-10-17T09:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T11:00:46.000Z","uid":372531,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"553a411f943884d4b8729d4532dd0ed3d6c0c279","tid":2246690,"uid":372531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"失業咗一個月，雖然一直已經揾緊工，但呢個時勢你哋都知道啦，in咗幾份全部衰哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後今日我老豆老母話而家警察canteen缺人手，佢哋話佢哋識人可以即刻挽位去做，屌你老母咁我梗係say no啦，寧願去洗碗都唔撚做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就俾兩老屌我喺屋企冇貢獻成個廢人咁<br />\n<br />\n我雖然知自己係廢柴，但都唔至於出賣良心去做呢啲嘢啦，仲衰過做雞，而家因為呢件事同屋企人嗌哂交，講明如果我唔做就唔畀我喺呢個企屋企住<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打絲打可以畀啲意見，我都唔知點處理好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 屋企兩老係黃絲，平時一講警察就幾撚賤幾撚廢，成日話撐後生仔"},{"pid":"c91cb084363bea6a1e924324d2951cb4cc552b7b","tid":2246690,"uid":76514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3a90ceae38120497292b216aac3720b3552751","tid":2246690,"uid":152790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"去做住先<br />\n記得注意衞生"},{"pid":"1d5a30899710a9cb9dfee5547813ad4f7ecbaec3","tid":2246690,"uid":236500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"在canteen 日日加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef68549777c3dd11f924a18c12271a727b873d4e","tid":2246690,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"你估你係警察咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5578a19f0a99ee36957c60dabeff46d9491ff55","tid":2246690,"uid":372531,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ef68549777c3dd11f924a18c12271a727b873d4e","tid":2246690,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":